ut not 3.0, 所以有無抄大家心裡有數."},{"pid":"9ab6cfc1d73e69660cdb13e0c3bbb8e77750c402","tid":2134763,"uid":111723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d85cd75fd30e73f9227aa2679ace4ab4e76e77c","tid":2134763,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"Bill Gates的公司Terrapower與中國國有企業「中國核工業集團」合作，共同研發核能技術。<br />\n「中國核工業集團」的業務包括民用及軍用核能技術。<br />\n目前該合作已經被美國當局終止，但Bill Gates表明，如果美國對華政策出現變化、掃清障礙之後，他會繼續推進該合作計劃。<br />\n難怪Bill Gates經常讚好中國，屬於半個護旗手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287060682219728902?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287060682219728902%3Fs%3D20&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=bb24e03d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1287060682219728902%3Fs%3D20&h=a1f3829d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1287060682219728902?s=20</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"#chinese digger"},{"pid":"1f4682764dc7326137321b7db7e3366003996652","tid":2134763,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f8213b07e0138bdc1055b94b9fe2c2575afb2d","tid":2134763,"uid":158499,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"e9247cda8de6fadffdf122b639690323d3bf7c29","tid":2134763,"uid":19557,"like":173,"dislike":15,"score":158,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"條友第一日已經係仆街黎 當年佢偷steve jobs 知識產權先有WINDOWS 既UI 先會有MOUSE 等等既野出現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"原來bill gates喺Apple做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"唔係咁解，睇睇 pirate of Silicon Valley ，會知多好多佢地後生的事跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7960ff189e2416e083187bf4d592615c398d11ba","tid":2134763,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"