地位。<br />\n所以microsoft實反硬美國制裁措施。<br />\n如果美國強硬，就搵全國最勁律師，告硬上法院，令所有制裁措施全部判違反美國憲法。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f500a0ee690333fe016edffc40b47c2e975105b2","tid":2134763,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2fdebd0620d506184588c52d7453adf1d8ecc2c","tid":2134763,"uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7130da39297ba3306c0750cb2d0f711d5981244b","tid":2134763,"uid":137248,"like":23,"dislike":5,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"樓主講到bill gate決定制唔制裁中國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實而家佢個project係因為美國制裁而停咗喎<br />\n掉撚轉晒黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:45:02.000Z","msg":"佢話如果美國制裁中國，就會重啟唔理美國反對喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"你有讀寫障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2f16a5260c1aa07cac358b32a3d5768d227304","tid":2134763,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79868410063d554f36e52b4118dff32c432ce333","tid":2134763,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"香港人：microsoft 仆街黎<br />\n香港人：我要打機，繼續用 windows"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:58:06.000Z","msg":"我用mac <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb99ee21ded4b2de80539d22114d1d1c6944da9","tid":2134763,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34c63b8970432575c67ad8787e064b7ceee37b91","tid":2134763,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人：microsoft 仆街黎<br />\n香港人：我要打機，繼續用 windows</blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2096565/page/14\" data-auto-link target